Let my list be list containing 10, 20, 30, 40, 50

Display "Testing basic indexing:"
Display my list[0]
Display my list[2]
Display my list[4]

Display "Testing natural language indexing:"
Display get item 1 from my list
Display get first item from my list
Display get last item from my list

Display "Testing postfix natural indexing:"
Display my list at index 3